Bug ticket creation
Project: GG Ops (GGO) ;
Issue Type: Bug ;
Summary;
Components: leave empty;
Description: Pre-condition , Expected  and Actual result , Steps to
reproduce ;
Fix versions: If the bug is related to an issue, then put this bug the same FixVersion as the main issue. Leave
this field empty if it is an unrelated bug;
Priority - specify priority;
Labels: leave empty;
Environment: QA , production ;
Attachments: video , screenshots , logs , etc;
Affects versions: leave empty;
Assignee: If the bug is related to an issue, then choose the same assignee as the main issue has. Otherwise
choose @Clapton Villanueva (Unlicensed)  as the assignee; 
Platform: iOS , Android , Windows , etc;
Department: Development  - for technical issues, LiveOps  - for game design, balance and assets
issues;
QA: If the bug is related to the main issue, put the same QA hero in the QA field as in main issue. In other
cases you can leave this field empty;
Priority Tag - specify priority tag.
Configurate Jira fields as follows:

Battle bonuses testing: 
1. Open the client's log file;
2. Play battle on the client;
3. Find this line in log file: "Battle: event #0"
4. Find lines like this: 12:36:49 :3 30123 > 1772 > unit 13 (wgd_archer_1) stats: count 9, hp 187,
melee attack 106, magic attack 106, melee def 101, magic def 227, speed 388, crit chance 98,
block chance 0, luck 157
5. Write this parameters down;
6. Use the bonuses;
7. Repeat this battle again with bonuses;
8. Refresh the client log and find the battle log again.
9. Compare the resulting parameters with those in p.4
Citadel Attack 
Camp Attack 
Citadel defence
Camp defence
